Package: SyntCF
Type: Package
Title: Synthetic Counterfactual for Program and Policy Evaluation based on Machine Learning
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Ahmed T. Hammad [aut, cre]
Maintainer: The package maintainer <ahmed.t.hammad@gmail.com>
Description: The SyntCF package provides a set of tools to estimate the effect of a 
    program or a policy using a robust time series synthetic counterfactual approach
    coupled with the double difference estimator within a Machine Learning framework.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
